title: Official Australian Government information
description: The official Australian Government response website to provide support and updates to Australians on the Coronavirus pandemic.
cleaned_text: The 2023 Federal Budget has been handed down. You can find all Budget papers at www.budget.gov.au 9 May 2023 On 25 October 2022, Medibank Private advised that more data has potentially been compromised than originally thought, and affects both AHM and Medibank Private customers. If you think you may be affected, it's important to act quickly. For further guidance, visit [https://www.cyber.gov.au/acsc/view-all-content/alerts/medibank-private-cyber-security-incident](https://www.cyber.gov.au/acsc/view-all-content/alerts/medibank-private-cyber-security-incident) If you are planning to travel, make sure you stay up to date with state and territory information below.
